{"tid":2450127,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Line 中國聯營技術人員可查看日本用戶資料","createTime":"2021-03-17T07:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T07:42:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1c29a3deee228da2ed210094c6b566cf3b6dcc3e","tid":2450127,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:21:22.000Z","msg":"即時通訊軟件 Line 周三 （ 3 月 17 日）公佈，其在中國的聯營公司的技術人員可存取用戶個人資料數據，引發私隱問題。<br />\n<br />\n據了解， 4 名於上海的 Line 聯營公司技術員工自 2018 年起可存取日本 Line 用戶的個人資料。涉及的數據包括用戶姓名、電話號碼、帳號，以及一些未被加密的通話紀錄。<br />\n<br />\nLine 指，容許聯營公司人員取得其客戶資料是工作所需，又強調沒有違規，但《日經亞洲評論》指，Line 的私隱政策未有充份披露有關外國人員可存取資料。現時 Line 已向日本個人資料保護委員會匯報此事，以及終止上海聯營公司存取該數據的權限，並成立獨立第三方小組調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/line-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%81%AF%E7%87%9F%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%AF%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2Fline-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%2587%259F%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E7%259C%258B%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%2F&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CT7KDDpXBBweeKWShnQU3kRY%3D&h=38b193ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2Fline-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%2587%259F%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%259F%25A5%25E7%259C%258B%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%2F&h=02575197\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/line-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%81%AF%E7%87%9F%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%AF%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99/</a>"},{"pid":"fe7e193f0c81b4acbeafab62f3c7b0c90b8f6ebd","tid":